info.author: Matthew Ballance
info.description:
PyVSC implements a Python-embedded domain-specific language for
  capturing random variables and data structures, constraints,
  and functional coverage metrics. PyVSC is built on top of the
  Boolector SMT solver.
info.name: pyvsc
info.summary: pyvsc (Verification Stimulus and Coverage) is a Python package for generating randomized stimulus and defining and collecting functional coverage.
